It was good place to have hawaiian organic veggie food. I could spend time calmly.
Nice to see healthy options in Hawaii. I don’t have to ask for any substitutions when ordering for the kids. I love that there’s no sugar added in their smoothies and everything is natural.
The aloha bowl is wonderful
Unfortunately missed this little gem for years! A to go spot when in that hood!
Amazing HiBlend Açaí Bowl and Farm Gone Wild salad. The staff worked with my wife to make the salad with just the right ingredients and their suggestions were on point!

Awesome!! Gabby is cool

Surprisingly it’s One of the few spots to get a healthy meal on the island. They have vegan and plant based options and also serve bacon and eggs for those friends of yours that still eat dead animals. I had the Veganese salad that has mixed local greens from a local organic farm and had an amazing house made peanut dressing. Also had a organic coffee that uses locally grown Hawaiian coffee, really great!

Great place with fresh healthy food. Really satisfied and impressed. VEGAN friendly! They were super kind and made lots of accommodations and allowed me to check out labels/read ingredients. Key player in healthy food on the island. Good prices too. Thanks for feeding me!

Delicious healthy and super friendly
Wish I could give more than 5 stars. Their acai bowl is phenomenal! We also enjoyed their health shot, dragonfruit smoothie and ceaser wrap. Mahalo!
Perfect start to my morning! Mahalo
Food and smoothie was excellent!! 😁 Got the balt sandwich and dragonfruit smoothie.
great smoothies and good vibe.

The food is really fresh and tasty. They care about the environment by using biodegradable plates and utensils. The workers seem to take pride in their work because they are always keeping the establishment clean and tidy.

Do you want local ingredients delivered in unique delicious foods, smoothies & coffee? I know I do. And HiBlend delivers whole heartedly. They might be small but they pack a big punch. Parking is validated. Enjoy!
Place to small, service was bland! Not was expected when I seen all the reviews and ratings.
Great healthy tasting food and drinks.  Always quality eating!!
Amazing place! Awesome food! Locally owned local produce and delicious!!
Great customer service & tasty food. I had the Turkey Spinach Ceasar Wrap & it was very flavorful. Would definitely recommend.

One of my absolute favorite places to eat! Whether you are looking for a filling, delicious meal or a healthy treat, this is the place to go! They even have two locations now, one in town and the other in Wahiawa. One of the best Acai bowls you'll ever have. I tried the smoked salmon bacon sandwich and LOVED it even tho I don't normally care seafood. SO much variety!
Broke da Mouf Good Grub, Reasonably Priced, extremely convenient location across from Walmart🎯  Soon to be overrun as people discover this Hidden Gem⚡️

Good food, friendly staff. The food can take a long time to make sometimes but it’s worth the wait.The juices are pretty good too, especially the Candy Greens one. For food the spinach turkey wrap is the best.
Awesome food and staff! Also great to support local farms and business!

This place might not look the fanciest, but they're food is AMAZING and the restaurant is surprisingly cozy.  I got the spinach caesar wrap and cannot recommend it enough - usually wraps have way too much dressing, and not enough vegetables. This sandwich is the wrap of your DREAMS! Tons of veg, just the right amount of dressing, and very satisfying. Their smoothies look great too  - I'll definitely be coming back!

Great juice bar for freshly made real juice. Also makes delicious açai and smoothie bowls as well as salads and sandwiches. Highly recommend.
Absolutely amazing.  After a not so good dinner in typical Waikiki we searched for some good food today for lunch.  Wow 100 times better than last night.  Healthy and delicious!

nice place. the staff are friendly and will offer their suggestions if you ask. the food is delicious, just a bit pricey.

This place is really good. I ordere a turkey Caesar wrap today and it was so tasty. The service is fast and friendly. This is my new lunch go-to since I work in the area.
Best smoothie ever.

Every fruits and veggies organic and locally grown. All their food are generous portion,delicious and satisfying prepared to order.Variety Coffee selection also on point. The açai smoothies got me hooked every time. Thanks Hiblend looking forward to come here again on my next trip
Worth your time and money! The acai bowls are HUGE and packed with so many local healthy ingredients. I am one happy customer
Excellent ahi sandwich and poi pounder smoothy

Favorite smoothie spot by far. Excellent add ons available. Sandwiches are tasty, but for me it's the smoothies that set this place apart. I usually park at Ala Moana and walk; the big Walmart lot is also nearby. Please oh pretty please open a Chinatown location!

I give a 3-star review because I got a salad when I thought I ordered a wrap. It is partially my fault not to mention it. I didn’t ask the staff to redo my order but I simply asked her to give me a wrap separately. She was trying to charge me money for it and said fine afterward. I felt guilty for my mistake.  But the food is very tasty and healthy. I particularly like acai smoothies. I want to come back here for smoothies.
Delicious food with healthy options. Parking can sometimes be hard especially in the evening but worth the wait.
The salmon bacon sandwich was the best ever!!!!!!! Hands down!!!
Delicious! Staff there are nice & accommodating also.
Best turkey Cesar wrap I’ve ever had. Solid peppercorn dressing! Has a solid bite! And local farm sourced avocado is delicious 🙌
Really good healthy, fresh food.
The food here is so good. I recommend Hiblend for anyone who wants a great clean filling meal!
Best bowl there is!! Sandwiches are good too, and so is the coffee! Go, don't think twice!

I discovered this place late on my trip. However, once I discovered it, I went there everyday for the rest of my stay in Oahu for their smoothie. I tried the Poi Pounder & Red Dragon smoothie & they were delicious. It is a small clean shop with parking on the vicinity. If you are picking up & not dining in, then you don't have to pay for parking. There is also meter parking available on the street.
Great staff and healthy options love the bowls and sandwiches are amazing
Delicious food and very friendly staff.
Some the best things in Life, are rarely found & to be experienced. This fine place is one of thous places...
Absolutely yummy, try the hiblend acai bowl!
The BALT was SO GOOD!!! 10/10 sandwich. The atmosphere is chill. Definitely the island vibe is was looking for in a health bar. Coming back for sure!
Deeelicious wraps! Went here twice for lunch as I couldn't resist and they did not disappoint! Only wish I'd found it sooner!!
Quick healthy great service
I loved this place! My dragonfruit bowl was amazing, the personal is friendly and the vibe is great. I'm happy I found them on this trip :)

This place is the best of the best.. Great health options, fast and awesome service. The bowls are amazing. And MOST of all please look into how much these guys do the the local community and how much they return back to their local system. Amazing business moto that Joey and his brothers have.
Their servis is great ,food as well. It's good for your health!!! I come here twice a week!!

We have gone to this place everyday after yoga since we landed. So happy we found this gem.  You have to try the roasted coconut coffee. It's to die for.  The green juices d9nt have enough kale in it but if u like a nice light green juice go for it. The salads and sandwiches are not to be missed.   Try the salmon bacon you will be surprised.
From the time they have opened I have been coming here and it is safe to say that their high standard of slow fresh food has continued on til this day. Great customer service
Amazing "the steamer" and delicious Dragon bowl!
Very good smoothies and juices. Fantastic sandwiches. Very good salads and salad wraps but they are also very expensive.
Great food, smoothies and Acai bowls! I always make sure to stop here when I visit Honolulu. If they had another location in Chicago I would eat there daily!

This place is the best. Great vibe with air conditioning, chill reggae music and the staff is on point! Kind, attentive, quick. As for the food... Seriously amazing salad, probably one of the best I've ever had. So much variety of yummy in there . Great healthy options. I also had a Turmeric smoothie, whhaa? It was spectacular as well. Come here. I'll be back during my stay.

Amazing organic food! They have a great selection for eating and drinking (juices, smoothies, teas, and coffee). Vegan options are available as well. I eat here regularly cause you can't fine organic food at such a comparable price.
Perfect
Everything really. All the food and drinks are delicious. Sometimes I come here 4 times a week, and the staff is always welcoming
Very good salads and wraps, but the wait can get a little out of hand during those peak hours like lunch. They'll validate your parking at the end of your meal. Seating can get full very fast too.

Yum Yum Yum - Dropped in a couple times last week while I was on vacation from Portland, OR. I was looking for something healthy organic and fresh, and let me tell all of you readers this is great food! We came in for both breakfast and lunch and both are a great value and tasty. Loved the BALT and turkey sandwiches. If you're in the area you gotta try this place!
Amazing farm to table cafe. I haven't tried the smoothies yet but the sandwiches are absolute delicious!!

The products are much better quality than in most of Honolulu, but you'll pay for it in prices and time. This restaurant is even slower than most local fast-casual establishments, which are notoriously slow. The food menu is limited, but what they have is good. Service is friendly but clearly disorganized.

I absolutely love this place, I don't love the prices (it's very expensive) but it's worth every dime. Amazingly fresh juices and smoothies. Delicious food. I just wish I could come more often. Staff is also amazingly friendly and helpful. The location isn't the easiest to park at (just park at Walmart and walk).
SO GOOD!!!! So so good!

Healthy! Quick! Convenient!  Of course to eat ACTUAL food, you have to shed a little more cash. Which isn't too bad if you do this once in a while.  I had a delicious pitaya red dragon smoothie, and 6$ wasn't too bad! I'm looking forward to swinging thru.

Super yummy sandwich! All ahi menus were sold out so I took salmon avocado sandwich with garlic source. Really yummy. Definitely worth visiting again to try ahi sandwich. The guy told me ahi arrives at the cafe weekly on Friday, so ahi might be sold out on Wednesday and Thursday.
Super healthy AND good. Lots of options. Fresh ingredients!! Very nice people. Went nearly every day when visiting.
Tiny shop with a dine in area which serves fresh healthy options. The green giant is a must try! 👍
I had the red Dragon smoothie. It hit the spot and was so yummy!! Everyone there was very nice and helpful.
Nice hidden spot. Good vibe.
